"""
NBA Stats Dashboard CLI

Usage:
    ./nba --help                    # Show all commands
    ./nba player --help             # Player commands
    ./nba team --help               # Team commands
    ./nba collect --help            # Collection commands
    ./nba ml --help                 # ML pipeline commands
    ./nba scrape --help             # Props scraping commands

Examples:
    ./nba player update "LeBron James"
    ./nba player game-logs
    ./nba team defense
    ./nba collect injuries
    ./nba ml pipeline --dry-run
    ./nba scrape all
"""

